{
  "text": "At baseline, 84 (64.1 %) had detectable HHV DNA in their seminal plasma including: EBV (27.5 %), HSV-1/2 (2.3 %), CMV (51.9 %), HHV-6 (6.9 %), HHV-7 (8.4 %), HHV-8 (3.1 %) [CITATION_1] (Table 1) .",
